      <span class="eyebrow">Still unsure?</span>
      <h2>
        The easiest next step is to describe the project in practical terms.
      </h2>
      <p>
        Share what is changing, what is not working, what kind of property it
        is, and what timing matters. That is usually enough to point you in the
        right direction quickly.
      </p>
      <ul class="value-list">
        <li>Photos help when available.</li>
        <li>Scope questions are welcome before booking.</li>
        <li>Urgent electrical concerns should be called or texted directly.</li>
      </ul>
